snippet.textDisplay: I had to circle back to this video as I've just now as of 3 minutes ago upgraded my iPhone 8 to an iPhone 17. I never intended to rock my iPhone 8 for so many years but after 2 years it was still perfectly fine so I had no reason to upgrade but maybe 2 years ago I started noticing that the battery was really starting to fade but I had no money and was in between jobs so a new phone just wasn't going to happen and then this year I've noticed that several apps have been notifying me that they will no longer support either my phone or the version of iOS on my phone so I knew I needed to get a new phone. I honestly wasn't even planning on getting the 17 as I just wanted something newer than the phone that I had but when I went on my provider's website it became very obvious that the iPhone 17 was the best deal to be had and I ended up buying it while remembering very little about it so now I'm circling back to this video to refresh my memory.
